Abbreviations for text editor SciTE via Zen Coding

HOW-TO
There two abbreviations files. One works with HTML only, other - with CSS only.
Put their into your home directory, then open .SciTEUser.properties and put these two lines:

abbreviations.*.css=$(SciteUserHome)/css.abbrev.properties
abbreviations.*.html=$(SciteUserHome)/html.abbrev.properties

You can find .SciTEUser.properites at menu (SciTE menu -> Options -> open User Options File), or create it at home directory.

